reviews.review_text: Best run These shows at the HJK were for me the best shows in one venue combined...camping allowed on site..good vibes..the band was having a great time..I went for the first show and stayed the whole week

Agree with below commentor The Kaiser was so much fun included everything. Camping a bar volleyball the band loved it also. As one can tell by the set lists and energy in the crowd every night. This show was more fun due to the X factor not knowing what was coming next was what we...( I ) Followed them for year after year night after night. Sound here is good. I give it 4 stars for the music and 1 Star for the fun we had.
